thread.title_full: Texas OL uncertain for TCU game with knee injury | Dallas Morning News

author: Chuck Carlton
title: Texas OL uncertain for TCU game with knee injury
text:
Starting right tackle Kent Perkins is listed as day-to-day after suffering a knee injury against Oklahoma State, coach Charlie Strong said. Texas visits TCU on Saturday.
"I just don't know how serious it is," Strong said, adding that a helmet hit Perkins' knee. Without Perkins, Texas had minus-11 yards on 16 plays against Oklahoma State.
